  "prompt": "Can we load money in multi wallet ICICI card?",
  "response": "As of my last update in October 2023, ICICI Bank offers various types of cards, including multi-wallet cards. However, the specific features and functionalities can vary depending on the card type and the bank's policies.\n\nTypically, multi-wallet cards are prepaid cards that can be loaded with money and used across multiple wallets or accounts. These cards can be used for different purposes, such as travel, shopping, and dining, each with its designated wallet.\n\nTo load money onto a multi-wallet ICICI card, you would usually follow these steps:\n\n1. **Online Banking**: Log in to your ICICI Bank account through internet banking or the mobile app. Navigate to the prepaid card section, select your multi-wallet card, and choose the option to load money. Enter the amount and confirm the transaction.\n\n2. **Branch Visit**: Visit an ICICI Bank branch and request to load money onto your multi-wallet card. You may need to fill out a form and provide identification.\n\n3. **Customer Service**: Contact ICICI Bank customer service for assistance and guidance on loading money onto your card.\n\n4. **ATM**: Some multi-wallet cards might allow loading money via ICICI Bank ATMs, though this is less common.\n\nPlease note that specific procedures and options might vary, so it is advisable to check the latest details directly with ICICI Bank or refer to their official website or customer support for the most accurate information.",
